methods.isResolvable:
Returns true if the resolver can resolve the uri.

:param uri: (java.net.URI) - the uri
:return: (boolean) true if this resolver can resolve uri
methods.resolve:
Resolve uri into an object.

:param uri: (java.net.URI) - the URI
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.Table) the object

text:
The parquet table resolver is able to resolve local parquet files, or directories for the scheme "parquet",
 into tables.

 
 For example, parquet:///data/my-file.parquet or parquet:///data/my-dir.

 
 For more advanced use cases, see ParquetTools.
